  ('dietitian-moex-01056', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-111-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '重症病人常見之營養診斷（nutritiondiagnosis），下列何者最不適當？', '["不足或過多的腸道或靜脈營養供給", "蛋白質營養需求增加", "腸道功能異常", "低白蛋白血症之蛋白質營養不良"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:53+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e3564b4d13aa", "answer_pdf_sha1": "08ee67449858", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111030", "c": "103", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
